## Quick Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| Jenkins won't start | Check Java 21 installed, check override.conf |
| SonarQube won't start | Add swap, set vm.max_map_count=524288 |
| Quality Gate timeout | Check SonarQube webhook URL is correct |
| Ansible WAR not found | Run Maven build first in Jenkins pipeline |
| App not showing | Check Tomcat is running on VM3 port 8080 |
| Not Authorized SonarQube | Update sonar-token credential in Jenkins |
